  "title": "PLATING MAINTENANCE TECHNICIAN",
  "description": "<p><strong>To Be Accomplished :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Organize the maintenance schedule for all equipment in Plating</li>\n  <li>Carry out installation and modification of machines and equipment</li>\n  <li>Carry out all general maintenance work on plating line equipment, ie motor, pump rectifier etc.</li>\n  <li>Carry out general electrical works, repairs, troubleshooting and maintenance of machines and equipment.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with vendor to do repair on equipment or process, cleanness</li>\n  <li>Purchase component and spare part related to electrical and control item to minimize the cost</li>\n  <li>Daily / periodic check, record and feedback all plating equipment for continuous operation</li>\n  <li>Support DI/waste treatment operation</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Electrical or Mechanical</li>\n  <li>More than 3 years of working experience in maintenance environment</li>\n  <li>Able to read electrical drawing and Autocad experience</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently with minimum guidance.</li>\n  <li>Able to communicate effective</li>\n  <li>12 hours shift: 4 day work week</li>\n  <li>Willing to overtime when required</li>\n</ul>",
